Class HwmfPalette.WmfSelectPalette

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwmf.record.HwmfPalette.WmfSelectPalette
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord, HwmfRecord
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HemfPalette.EmfSelectPalette
    Enclosing class:
    HwmfPalette 

    public static class HwmfPalette.WmfSelectPalette
extends java.lang.Object
implements HwmfRecord
    The META_SELECTPALETTE record defines the current logical palette with a specified Palette Object.(META_SEN CTPALETTE记录用指定的收件箱对象定义当前逻辑调色板。)

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      protected int paletteIndex
      A 16-bit unsigned integer used to index into the WMF Object Table to get the Palette Object to be selected.(一个16位无符号整元，用于索引到WMF对象表中以获取要选择的收件箱对象。)
